<s> In English it is customary to place two spaces after a period at the end of  </s>
<s> a sentence.  </s>
<s> However, current HTML browsers generally squeeze spaces into a  </s>
<s> single space, so a paragraph like this one would be displayed with only one  </s>
<s> space between sentences.  </s>
<s> Some current WYSIWYG HTML editors cover for this by changing the first space  </s>
<s> to a non-breaking space (&amp;nbsp;).  </s>
<s> This forces the browser to display two spaces.  </s>
<s> I noticed that Amaya will change the NBSP-SP sequence into two regular spaces.  </s>
<s> That is to say, if I read in a document with the NBSP-SP sequence and then save it again the sequence is changed to SP-SP.  </s>
