<s> Only on a typewriter, as typewriters must use monospaced fonts.  </s>
<s> In electronic typesetting, one uses an extended space after a period (I've never worked with metal type, so I don't remember if one used two en-spaces or a special double-en-space or some such piece of type).  </s>
<s> Word processors automatically extend the space after a period, as do web browsers.  </s>
<s> I'd suggest checking a book on typography out of the library if you're interested in an extended discussion of this.  </s>
